{"tid":268082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句對人生有影響力既說話","createTime":"2017-06-02T17:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T13:51:29.000Z","uid":22992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ec552eb089c4aa665617af90c5e78928aa8959","tid":268082,"uid":22992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"你要做一個不動聲色的大人了。不準情緒化，不準偷偷想念，不準回頭看。去過自己另外的生活。你要聽話，不是所有的魚都會生活在同一片海裏。<br />\n<br />\n村上春樹"},{"pid":"81df44a6d5227eb536153c809d727bd9525a8fc4","tid":268082,"uid":8679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"快高長大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361d02fc77bedefc5358969754c51abd3a73b118","tid":268082,"uid":73844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"願你走出半生，歸來仍是少年。"},{"pid":"e67a1ed5d6ed1b8763fdb0f68cce1e272ff5d9b0","tid":268082,"uid":71214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"人生就是一場挑戰"},{"pid":"8fbed4e7eab0aba7c96716949ab47de08fe7c0a3","tid":268082,"uid":119850,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我們一路奮戰，不是為了改變世界，而是為了不讓世界改變我們。&rdquo;-----《熔爐》"},{"pid":"d2845010f60c7fa16f1aa5622613d5e05a0a1a42","tid":268082,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"I suppose in the end, the whole of life becomes an act of letting go, but what always hurts the most is not taking  a moment to say goodbye.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2051dfeb78c6b80c76089a7a01474a2ce67dd415","tid":268082,"uid":99629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:52:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">活在當下</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c552631bb734d5d66f4b4cdf5729b4978ad3930","tid":268082,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"有勇氣自殺 無勇氣生存?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3939d06f21df319b37e700678c69fa7348d66bf4","tid":268082,"uid":27728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>願你走出半生，歸來仍是少年。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2f6a99c6d79586cd460cad17da1a00c54eda8f","tid":268082,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"Don't burn your opportunity for a temporary comfort"},{"pid":"3d4d0116098615d3a80ee703f893ca0b5816c416","tid":268082,"uid":86972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"Just Do It<br />\nDon't Let Your Dreams be Dreams"},{"pid":"20a65f896ec71a305602b07fcd05c6654d4faf3b","tid":268082,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"我有幾句<br />\n<br />\n「不往前邁進步伐，就無法開拓道路。鼓起勇氣付諸行動的結果，怎可以讓它變成悲劇」<br />\n<br />\n「再狼狽也要勇敢地走下去。<br />\n可以試了一輩子都不成功，但不可以失敗後讓自己腐敗。」<br />\n<br />\n「痛苦的時候，能拯救自己的也只有自己；<br />\n想要什麼，目標在哪裡，也只有自己才會知道。」"},{"pid":"6dbc5df45a1b658ee5cd4493204400930b9a678a","tid":268082,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"入黎仲未見到 <br />\n金句post指定金句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機會係留比&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"29f29b66c2a331e842c4b2a9a3e4da574917ff87","tid":268082,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"樓上以為自己好撚風趣